This python application is built using python 2.4, cherrypy 2.2.1 and pysqlite 2.2.2. You'll need them (or equivalent) before you run it. 
I found all were available as native builds for Intel Mac

http://www.python.org/
http://www.cherrypy.org/
http://pysqlite.org/

To build a dummy database cd to the src directory and run:
	> python CreateSiteDB.py 
	
To start the server cd to the src directory and run:
	> python Site.py